<typeStatus box="[1183,1236,909,933]" pageId="40" pageNumber="39">type</typeStatus>
species name.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="40.[192,1034,956,981]" box="[192,1034,956,981]" pageId="40" pageNumber="39">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[192,432,956,980]" pageId="40" pageNumber="39">Species included.</emphasis>
The 
<typeStatus box="[493,546,957,981]" pageId="40" pageNumber="39">type</typeStatus>
species and 
<taxonomicName authority="Plotz, 1883" authorityName="Plotz" authorityYear="1883" box="[701,1031,956,981]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Hesperia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="40" pageNumber="39" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dares">
<emphasis box="[701,884,956,980]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="39">Hesperia dares</emphasis>
Plötz, 1883
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="40.[192,831,1005,1029]" box="[192,831,1005,1029]" pageId="40" pageNumber="39">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[192,380,1005,1029]" pageId="40" pageNumber="39">Parent taxon.</emphasis>
